eplyTime":"2017-03-16T18:14:27.000Z","msg":"[quote]<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pkcuw3fb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpkcuw3fb&h=8ee1abd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9508d2bc332dd753a2624b0d12bf47e8e4da5f23","tid":159021,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:17:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n軍事人才<br />\n呢班先係真本土<br />\n咁多年默默培育軍人</blockquote><br />\n家長簽同意書果陣撚有同意送個仔/女去軍事訓練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢夠膽大大隻字寫明軍事訓練<br />\n然後比人自由揀去唔去<br />\n睇有邊個家長肯制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n軍事訓練都講得出真係膠都費事畀<br />\n點做pr"},{"pid":"02d64a965b14987b1c2730cc776ad1e19180df77","tid":159021,"uid":73705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:19:51.000Z","msg":"食屎啦成班人係到講大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  做過唔肯認，驚自己老到捱唔到啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"2795a3befac3e602f4a3c0cfecd5cc88e8b64733","tid":159021,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:30:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有哂圖都可以否認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那人思維嘛，啲老而不全部都噉諗嘢㗎啦<br />\n睇佢地啲答覆同睇民建聯或者人民日報冇分別</blockquote><br />\n明明有都話沒,指鹿為馬,係支那賤種特性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e49820a9d26ecda398b5abe08dbfc8cbeb2f23"